}

<div class="hero-section">
    <div>
        <h1>Welcome to Gym Frog</h1>
        <h2>Hop Your Way to Greatness</h2>
        <p>At Gym Frog, we don't just leap into fitness - we splash into it. Our trainers? They're hopping with enthusiasm. 
